#have_data

  %h2
    Have Data?

  %p
    Are you a researcher conducting acoustic telemetry studies within the #{t('project.location')}?  Are you ready to submit data about receiver locations (past, present, or future), or transmitters?  #{t('project.name')} wants you!

  %p
    - if can? :create, Submission
      %strong
        Last updated: Tuesday, May 22nd, 2012
      %br
      = link_to "Download", static_path("GLATOSWeb_Submission_Package.zip"), :target => '_blank'
      your #{t('project.name')} Data Submittal Package
      %br
      %br
      = link_to "Submit", new_submission_path
      your completed #{t('project.name')} Data Submittal Package
    - else
      The first step is to register as an Investigator
      = link_to "here.", new_user_registration_path
      Once your registration is approved, a link will appear on this page to download the #{t('project.name')} Data Submittal Package.

  %p
    The #{t('project.name')} Data Submittal Package contains templates for the entry of project information, proposed receiver deployments, actual receiver locations, and transmitter/tag details. The package, a compressed .ZIP archive, also contains descriptions of necessary and recommended data and instructions for entering information into the templates and for submittal of the formatted information to #{t('project.name')}.

  %p
    Please direct questions about data submittal to
    = link_to "#{t('project.contact.name')}", "mailto:#{t('project.contact.email')}"
